    "caption": "Scroll direction",
    "description": "Detects the direction of the vertical scroll and sets $:/temp/animate/scroll-direction to either "up" or "down". This can be used to animate the menu bar from the [[menubar plugin|$:/plugins/tiddlywiki/menubar]].   

<$link to="$:/temp/animate/scroll-direction" tag="code">$:/temp/animate/scroll-direction</$link> : {{$:/temp/animate/scroll-direction}}"
},

